snippet.title: Bokan Go Go Go (Sony Playstation JPN) Intro + Gameplay
snippet.description: Bokan Go Go Go is a kart racing game based on an anime. It's not very good and I definitely prefer the shooters. The courses are long and boring and the game is just slow. Have a look for yourself.
